#################################################################
#
#    FutuRaM Product / Component / Material / Element hierarchy
#
#    Class-based taxonomy extracted from the FutuRaM ontology.
#    Contains only owl:Class declarations, their rdfs:subClassOf
#    links within the futuram namespace, and rdfs:label. No
#    individuals, properties or external parents.
#
#    owl:imports the composition-statement TBox, which defines the
#    four roots (Product/Component/Material/Element) and the futuram
#    properties; the roots are not re-declared here.
#
#    Generated by extract_hierarchy.py (uv run + rdflib).
#
#################################################################

